[DAY 27] @Transactional ROLLBACK RULES:
  DEFAULT: rolls back on RuntimeException and Error.
  DEFAULT: does NOT roll back on checked Exception.

  OVERRIDES:
  rollbackFor = IOException.class     → also rollback on IOException
  rollbackFor = Exception.class       → rollback on ALL exceptions
  noRollbackFor = BusinessException   → don't rollback on this runtime exception

  RULE: If your @Transactional method declares a checked exception in 'throws',
        you MUST add rollbackFor = Exception.class or the specific type.

